Class FAKE_materials_quantumRendering

This is a fake extension. We've created it to verify the behavior of clients attempting to load a model which contains an extension that they do not support. By creating an extension which does not exist, we guarantee consistent results regardless of which client attempts to load a model requiring this extension.
